snippet.title: Star Wars Rogue Leaders (Unreleased) Wii Trailer
snippet.description:
Feast your eyes on gameplay from the completed -- but never released -- Rogue Squadron compilation for Nintendo Wii. 

This game was never officially announced by its developer or publisher, but it was openly rumored as a title in production by those close to the game. Its fate was thrown into turmoil with the closing of development studio Factor 5 in 2008. Hopes for its release lived for a short time afterwards as negotiations continued on plans to finish the product with a partner studio. Despite this, the game sadly was never released.
